Since `RCLike.re g x` is measurable, `neg (RCLike.re g x)` is measurable.
`Real.toNNReal` is continuous, so `Real.toNNReal (neg (RCLike.re g x))` is measurable.
Therefore, `g₂` is `Measurable`.

Now we can apply `helper`.
```tactics
