  apply Measurable.neg
  exact h1
```
Now, `g₂` is `Real.toNNReal` applied to `h2`. `Real.toNNReal` is continuous.
```tactics
have h3 : Measurable (fun x => Real.toNNReal (- RCLike.re (g x))) := by
  apply Measurable.toNNReal
  exact h2
```
The function `g₂` is equal to `fun x => Real.toNNReal (- RCLike.re (g x))`.
```tactics
exact h3
```

